---

<section class="workflow-section" data-test="workflow-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Four skills. One methodology.</h2>
    <p class="workflow-intro">RootSpec works through four composable skills that take you from idea to validated implementation.</p>
    <div class="workflow-steps">
      <div class="workflow-step" data-test="workflow-step-init">
        <div class="step-number">01</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-command"><code>/rs-init</code></div>
          <h3>Initialize</h3>
          <p>Scaffold the RootSpec directory structure and wire up validation hooks in your project.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="workflow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
      <div class="workflow-step" data-test="workflow-step-spec">
        <div class="step-number">02</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-command"><code>/rs-spec</code></div>
          <h3>Specify</h3>
          <p>Turn a product description into a five-level spec — philosophy, truths, interactions, systems, and implementation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="workflow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
      <div class="workflow-step" data-test="workflow-step-impl">
        <div class="step-number">03</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-command"><code>/rs-impl</code></div>
          <h3>Implement</h3>
          <p>Build the feature with the spec as ground truth. Every decision traces back to a principle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="workflow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
      <div class="workflow-step" data-test="workflow-step-validate">
        <div class="step-number">04</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-command"><code>/rs-validate</code></div>
          <h3>Validate</h3>
          <p>Run automated acceptance tests derived from the spec. Pass or fail — no ambiguity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .workflow-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .workflow-intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .workflow-steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .workflow-step {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 160px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .workflow-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    align-self: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .step-number {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  .step-command {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step-command code {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .workflow-step h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .workflow-step p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .workflow-steps {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .workflow-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      align-self: flex-start;
      margin-left: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
